*% -------------------------------------------------------------------------
*% Munbyn ITPP941 PPD adapted for Linux / stock CUPS rastertolabel.
*% Derived from the working macOS queue ("Munbyn Label printer", edivista PPD).
*% Two changes vs. the macOS PPD:
*%   1. *cupsModelNumber 20 -> 18  (stock rastertolabel: ZEBRA_ZPL = 0x12 = 18)
